  "prompt": "Which is a suitable solar panel installation provider near San Gabriel, California CA?",
  "response": "Finding a suitable solar panel installation provider near San Gabriel, California, involves considering factors such as reputation, customer reviews, certifications, and services offered. Here are some reputable solar installation companies in the area:\n\n### 1. **SunPower by The Green Power**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: SunPower is one of the most well-known solar companies in the U.S., offering high-efficiency panels and comprehensive warranties.\n   - **Location**: Serves San Gabriel and surrounding areas.\n   - **Website**: [sunpower.com](https://www.sunpower.com)\n\n### 2. **Sunrun**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: Sunrun is a leading provider of residential solar panels and offers flexible financing options, including solar leases and power purchase agreements (PPAs).\n   - **Location**: Widely available in California, including San Gabriel.\n   - **Website**: [sunrun.com](https://www.sunrun.com)\n\n### 3. **PetersenDean Roofing & Solar**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: PetersenDean is a California-based company offering both roofing and solar services, making them a good choice if you need both.\n   - **Location**: Serves Southern California, including San Gabriel.\n   - **Website**: [petersendean.com](https://www.petersendean.com)\n\n### 4. **Solar Optimum**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: Solar Optimum specializes in high-quality solar installations with a focus on customer satisfaction and offers competitive pricing.\n   - **Location**: Serves the Greater Los Angeles area, including San Gabriel.\n   - **Website**: [solaroptimum.com](https://www.solaroptimum.com)\n\n### 5. **NRG Clean Power**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: NRG Clean Power offers a range of solar solutions and has a strong reputation for customer service and reliable installations.\n   - **Location**: Serves the San Gabriel Valley and surrounding areas.\n   - **Website**: [nrgcleanpower.com](https://www.nrgcleanpower.com)\n\n### 6. **Semper Solaris**\n   - **Why Choose Them**: Semper Solaris offers solar, roofing, and battery storage solutions, with a focus on military veterans and their families.\n   - **Location**: Serves Southern California, including San Gabriel.\n   - **Website**: [sempersolaris.com](https://www.sempersolaris.com)\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Right Provider:\n   - **Get Multiple Quotes**: Compare quotes and services from at least three different providers.\n   - **Check Reviews**: Look at customer reviews on platforms like Yelp, Google, and the Better Business Bureau (BBB).\n   - **Verify Certifications**: Ensure the company is certified by the North American Board of Certified Energy Practitioners (NABCEP).\n   - **Ask About Financing**: Inquire about financing options, including loans, leases, and PPAs.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, you may want to contact these providers directly or use online tools like EnergySage to compare local installers.",
